description:
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Open Day Saturday 21st November 10-1pm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a qualified Radiographer, or a Student Radiographer looking for a new opportunity in 2021? Do you want to work at a “Good” Hospital (CQC rating 2020) Then come along on the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;21st November 2019 from 10am-1pm &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;and meet the Medical Imaging Team at Mid-Cheshire Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have Band 5 vacancies for enthusiastic, ambitious candidates to join our friendly and forward-thinking department. Saturday 21st November is an opportunity for you to discuss the start of your career or your continual professional development with our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MCHFT was rated “Good” by the CQC during the inspection in 2020, and recently we were named as one of the best hospitals in the country (CHKS Top Hospital for 2019). The Radiology department has been recognised as the Best Training Placement for Radiologist Registrars for the last 3 years.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On the 21st November we would like to introduce you to our department, our service vision and our aims. We will be offering tours of the department, you will be able to meet our teams and we will have support available to discuss relocation and if you would like to have an interview on the day we can arrange that too!!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; The Medical Imaging Department has had major investment in CT &amp; MRI, and has recently purchased 6 new DR mobiles. In 2021we will be upgrading our last few non digital general rooms to DR and we will be opening a new Emergency Department CT and X ray room.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We provide a 24/7 CT and Plain film service and successful candidates will be expected to participate in the out of hour’s rota.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer an attractive benefits package including an excellent pension scheme, gym membership, discounts on days out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information on our open day please contact&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Angela Hutchinson Deputy Service manager 01270273367&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Angela.hutchinson@mcht.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
